---- MODULE MCDieHarder ----
(*******************************)
(* The following definitions duplicate the original                     *) 
Die Hard problem.   However, TLC does not allow one to write          *)   
function-valued expressions in a configuration file; so we use this      *)      
module and have it extend module DieHarder to define functions         *)       
MCCapacity and MCJug that are substituted for Capacity                  *)          
and Jug, respectively.   Since TLC needs the value of Jug              *)           
to determine what values should be used in defining MCCapacities       )*            
(which is a function having domain {0..2}), we also define MCJug and    ) *               tell                  it to substitute for Jug.)*)   (******************************)
